        "body": "Your first paycheck comes with a plot twist: the number in your contract is not the number that lands in your bank account.\n\nA chunk goes to taxes — the shared bill for schools, roads, hospitals, and the firefighters you hopefully never need.\n\nYou can't skip taxes, but you can understand them. People who do plan better, dodge nasty surprises, and keep more of what they work for."
