        "title": "You can't cram a vibe",
        "body": "You just spent a whole course learning to name feelings, pause before reacting, read people, repair after a fight.\n\nHere's the catch: you can't cram emotional intelligence the night before a hard conversation. Emotions move fast and your old habits run on autopilot.\n\nReal change doesn't come from trying harder in the heated moment. It comes from small reps, repeated until they become **who you are**.",
