        "body": "Don't try to overhaul your whole emotional life by Friday. That's how people burn out and quit.\n\nPick **one** tiny practice and only that:\n- A 10-second feelings check-in each day\n- One pause before reacting\n- One I-statement this week\n\nTiny is the point. A habit small enough to feel almost silly is a habit small enough to actually keep."
